1985, c. 6, s. 219; 1992, c. 11, s. 21; 2021, c. 27, s. 67.

220. The member of the Bureau d’évaluation médicale shall study the submitted record. Where he deems it expedient, he may examine the worker or require any medical information or document from the Commission that it holds or may obtain regarding the worker.
